Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,------------------ANIME-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.34,0:00:22.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小妹妹  你有空吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.40,0:00:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要和我去玩玩？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:32.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(310,325)\fs14}doppelgänger
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:32.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道「分身」一说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.27,0:00:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分…？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.48,0:00:37.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一个自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁要是看见了  灾厄将会降临其身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.16,0:00:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  瞎说啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.53,0:01:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.59,0:01:09.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帅呆了  你看见他那表情了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.59,0:01:12.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.81,0:01:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就和他说了几句话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.38,0:01:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后他自己就对号入座了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.40,0:01:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.17,0:01:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.93,0:01:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是叫针眼来着？眼皮都肿了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.62,0:01:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该很快就会好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.53,0:01:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这倒是  不过很不方便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.98,0:03:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下个月就升到三年级了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.53,0:03:33.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  到时候也十五岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.72,0:03:34.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.83,0:03:37.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒不是不好  觉得没什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.39,0:03:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如中考之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.35,0:03:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  别让我想起来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:50.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件是不是太花俏了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.52,0:03:55.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点土
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.78,0:03:58.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？我倒是不讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:02.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是要买给我的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我要穿啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用老是照镜子很轻松吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有这用法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.18,0:04:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轮廓不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着有点来气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.03,0:04:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真土
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太过分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.22,0:04:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.49,0:04:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.14,0:04:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像「来辨真假」一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:49.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.11,0:04:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  你好像说过能看见什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:04:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.09,0:05:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我身上也能看到什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.77,0:05:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.23,0:05:10.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这双眼  我觉得很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.98,0:05:13.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左右眼的颜色不同感觉很美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.61,0:05:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是叫异色症来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫双色瞳啥的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.69,0:05:20.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遮起来太浪费了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.31,0:05:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多可爱的脸蛋就这么白费了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:27.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这不是在绕着弯子说自己也可爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.79,0:05:30.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  这我不否定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.26,0:05:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔  给我那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:47.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？为什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:53.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切  那只娃娃那么可爱的说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未咲对可爱的认知有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:05:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个可爱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.87,0:06:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个丑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:04.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么那边的象呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:12.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是不懂你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想去更好一点的游乐园啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.84,0:06:22.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下周怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.97,0:06:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下周妈妈因为人偶的展览会要去东京  所以不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.58,0:06:29.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我得一个人看家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:30.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.67,0:06:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姨妈不在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.67,0:06:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就去你家玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.76,0:06:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.13,0:06:45.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到咯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.08,0:06:47.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.74,0:06:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四月天还下雪真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.53,0:06:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣真幸福  家里有好多漂亮的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.53,0:07:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄弟姐妹  算不算二代血亲来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.31,0:07:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血亲？啊是的  二代血亲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.97,0:07:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈和爸爸是一代血亲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷奶奶是二代血亲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:12.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那兄弟姐妹应该也是二代血亲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.01,0:07:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.37,0:07:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在新的班级里  那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有在传这些事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.76,0:07:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  新的班级怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.26,0:07:27.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有帅哥吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:28.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是觉得  这个班级有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.17,0:07:34.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.79,0:07:36.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点像「被诅咒了」的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被诅咒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:45.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  这种类似的传言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那确实有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.93,0:07:49.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没帅哥吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要给你介绍一个？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:55.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,介绍啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:07:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  男生啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.50,0:07:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是说没帅哥吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.03,0:08:05.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未咲  你像做媒人的大妈一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.79,0:08:07.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是大妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.18,0:08:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里我还是头一次来  好壮观
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.65,0:08:20.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么  好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.87,0:08:21.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是幸代姨妈做的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈呢  希望你能原谅她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是指光代姨妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.32,0:08:44.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是姨妈  也是你妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.53,0:08:47.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么原谅不原谅的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈现在还把鸣当做自己的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.02,0:08:55.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也真的很想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.88,0:09:00.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过因为让别人收养你  心里感到愧疚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.74,0:09:04.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有让鸣离开自己身边而产生的罪恶感  所以说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:07.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我知道她很难过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.57,0:09:09.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.51,0:09:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有埋怨过她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且要说到心里感到愧疚的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.05,0:09:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雾果…妈妈也是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.69,0:09:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从双胞胎姐妹那里夺走了孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.61,0:09:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  更多的是害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,担心我会回到我亲生母亲身边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.61,0:09:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以也禁止我们俩见面？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.67,0:09:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈的想法也可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不习惯的话  这个地方待久了可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.07,0:09:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去楼上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.51,0:09:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为人偶是空虚的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大  好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:10:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.69,0:10:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的房间就只有四畳半的空间外加一套被褥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.42,0:10:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.45,0:10:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也好想有这样一个房间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  你也不是小孩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:10:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别摆姐姐的架子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.03,0:10:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可是双胞胎  不分大小的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说先出世的就是姐姐么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:25.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不管
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:31.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该力气大的才是姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.11,0:10:33.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这什么理论…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.46,0:10:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是姐姐了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.97,0:10:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.90,0:10:43.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勤劳少女可是很强的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在旁人看来就是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到蛮瘦的  放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.03,0:10:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不好说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.91,0:11:04.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我瘦可不代表你瘦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.50,0:11:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说啥  小家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢噢  发育了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.59,0:11:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.51,0:11:14.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别害羞嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.52,0:11:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未咲真是的  啥时候变成那种大叔了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:29.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们第几次一起洗澡来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.87,0:11:32.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小时候的就不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.31,0:11:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该有两三次吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.24,0:11:35.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是从什么时候开始的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小学五年级的时候来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.03,0:11:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  五年级的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天根婆婆一不小心说漏了嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:46.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是早就有点察觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.74,0:11:48.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么说也太像了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…也对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.93,0:11:53.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也觉得有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.03,0:11:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婴儿时候的照片一张也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:12:00.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我想不可能会丢掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在家里偷偷找了一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:03.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.36,0:12:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照片？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  刚出生时的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.23,0:12:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和鸣你并排照的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的长得一模一样  真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  明天去游乐场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我们以前和妈妈三个人一起去的游乐场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.42,0:12:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久以前的事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.85,0:12:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错没错  姨妈那次因为这事发了很大脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  真不明白那个时候她为什么那么生气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:36.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  就去那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.79,0:12:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.86,0:12:45.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣你有喜欢的人么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.54,0:12:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  未咲你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.73,0:12:49.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么样的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.49,0:12:53.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普普通通
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:56.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普普通通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.09,0:12:58.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  看着很老实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.03,0:13:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果是喜欢摇滚的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢的乐队一样是么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.04,0:13:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么喜欢他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.15,0:13:11.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有什么契机之类的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.57,0:13:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记不大清了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.28,0:13:17.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  刚才你说勤劳少女了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.83,0:13:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在打工么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.86,0:13:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  在附近的豆腐店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.89,0:13:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.36,0:13:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零用钱很紧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.59,0:13:40.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手机话费也不可小看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.69,0:13:44.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己玩的钱至少想要自己挣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.08,0:13:46.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未咲真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.31,0:13:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  马上就到爸爸的生日了  所以嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.50,0:13:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未咲和家人「相连」着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡着了么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.22,0:14:19.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.45,0:14:45.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.73,0:14:49.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不觉就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.69,0:14:57.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.82,0:15:01.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前来的时候还以为是个更大的游乐场
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.12,0:15:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们长大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:08.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此  时光的流逝可真残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.63,0:15:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.82,0:15:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去快要撞上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.75,0:15:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是千钧一发啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.23,0:15:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的鸣像姐姐一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.05,0:15:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔我来保护下未咲有何不可
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:15:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护什么的太夸张了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.41,0:16:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.27,0:16:12.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.18,0:16:18.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅仅是因为我的名字叫未咲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.80,0:16:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不是因为作为养女被送出去  那眼睛也不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你难道以为是自己的错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.15,0:16:26.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.69,0:16:30.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想法真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.74,0:16:34.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只眼睛是因为生病
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟养女什么的都无关  不是任何人的错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.77,0:16:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不管是未咲还是爸爸妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.37,0:16:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没有丝毫怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.29,0:16:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前也会想为什么只有我遭受这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.58,0:16:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我想结果还是一样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.23,0:16:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一样的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:03.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  如果是未咲作为养女被送出去  又失去左眼的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:08.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会像现在的未咲一样难过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以现在就挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:15.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:17.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.57,0:17:25.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  那边不就是未咲的家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.87,0:17:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜见山市真小
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.37,0:17:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.51,0:17:34.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之还是得离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.56,0:17:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢大城市吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:37.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那倒不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.75,0:17:38.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为学校
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学校？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:43.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…  我想学音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.10,0:17:44.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音乐大学？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.18,0:17:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.99,0:17:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能成功
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要是减肥了就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.52,0:18:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的  你比我还瘦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.75,0:18:21.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经够了  鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:25.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣也会跟着掉下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.61,0:18:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我绝不放手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.73,0:18:28.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要保护未咲…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.11,0:18:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.06,0:18:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.53,0:18:49.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:51.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.47,0:18:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.42,0:18:58.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到那么不起眼的刺激项目居然会那么口怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.87,0:19:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是可怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.36,0:19:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  你听懂了就行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.53,0:19:08.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前真害怕这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.65,0:19:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  是么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.78,0:19:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是挺喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.66,0:19:14.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣倒是意外的坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.04,0:19:16.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意外么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那样的感觉么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.87,0:19:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.56,0:19:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为死定了  真尽兴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.18,0:19:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说什么死的  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.80,0:19:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害我都没活着的实感
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.30,0:20:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.96,0:20:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在游乐场遇到那种事都没什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.68,0:20:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.04,0:20:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是那种担心的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.33,0:20:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是叫化疗吧？最近听说白血病是能治好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.23,0:20:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎就算药不起作用还有叫骨髓移植的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:32.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话从我这里抽就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.66,0:20:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医生也说从鸣身上抽是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.78,0:20:39.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出院之后再去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.62,0:20:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.91,0:20:49.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来马上就过生日了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.57,0:20:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么想要的么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.55,0:20:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣的生日也是一起的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.51,0:20:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要健康的未咲  如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.56,0:21:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是个难题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是在鸣家里看到的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.77,0:21:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我尽力试试
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.68,0:22:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.97,0:22:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  我说你…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.90,0:22:48.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.75,0:22:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣  见崎鸣
